Package org.jsonurl.factory Description

Defines generic value factory and parser interfaces, and provides a parser implementation built on the JsonUrlIterator interface.

If you need a parser bound to your own JSON object model API then you may implement a new ValueFactory and supply it to an instance of ValueFactoryParser. This is already done for J2SE datatypes and implemented in JsonUrlParser. Additionally, other artifacts do this for other object model APIs such as JSR-374 and json.org.
